        "cooked": "<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>Thanks for the response!</p>\n<p>The only thing I need is some kind of “reader” that retrieve the messages (through API if possible) for a certain group. I think this “reader” may perform as a “person” (phone number) because there is no way to create a “bot” (like in Slack)</p>\n<p>I’ll take a look the list you posted.</p>\n<p>Thanks!</p>\n<p>EDIT: <a href=\"https://github.com/signalapp/libsignal-service-java/blob/master/java/src/main/java/org/whispersystems/signalservice/internal/push/PushServiceSocket.java\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Here</a> there is some paths to the signal endpoint I guess</p>",
